I'd like to propose a different solution for jira (that of "Web interface should not use experimental API"): remove the `getJSON` call entirely. Now that we have paging on the server side for the DAGs list.

This diff in the template does the same as the JSON call, without an extra round trip:

```diff
diff --git a/airflow/www/templates/airflow/dags.html b/airflow/www/templates/airflow/dags.html
index ebf638f0..f78cce82 100644
