Hey that is why I created issue here, I solved my problem with custom type

```
var YieldYamlType = new yaml.Type('!yield', {
  kind: 'mapping',
  construct: function (data) {
    try {
      const { val, inc = 1} = data;
      if (val instanceof Serial) {
        return val.next(inc);
      }
      return Number(val) + inc
    }catch(exp){ return data }
  },
});
``` 
And you can use it like this
value: !yield { val: 5, inc: 10 } // ==> 5 +10

